 Megan Huntsman , 40 , is facing life in prison after pleading guilty to killing the six newborns , then stashing their bodies in the garage of her home in Pleasant Grove , Utah .
A judge handed Huntsman six sentences of five years to life - she will spend at least 15 years in prison .
Huntsman was a meth addict , told police that she started killing off her children when she got pregnant because her drug problem .
Her estranged husband Darren West , found the bodies in her garage .